I think of life as something that can be developed in 5 different areas:
  • Personal
  • -- relationships (family, friendships, romantic)
  • -- finances
  • -- health
  • -- spiritulality (meditation)
  • Education
  • Business (Career and Work)
  • Athletics
  • Volunteering/Community service
  • Arts
Thinking of my life allows me to better myself in every area. Can you be split it further?
Sure, but for me, there's almost no reason to. I can look at this, see how much time I spend on each of them, and decide if I have my priorities straight or not.
